# TekConsult Project - Knowledge Transfer (KT) Document

## 1. Project Overview
TekConsult is a digital consultation marketplace connecting users with professional consultants across various categories. Users can search for experts, book sessions, and engage via real-time chat or voice calls.

## 2. Technology Stack

### Backend
- **Framework**: .NET 10.0 Web API
- **Database**: SQL Server with Entity Framework Core (EF Core)
- **Real-time Communication**: SignalR (Chat, Notifications, Session Control)
- **Authentication**: JWT (JSON Web Tokens) with OTP-based login (Email/Phone)
- **Architecture**: Service-Oriented Architecture (Controller -> Service -> Repository/Context)

### Frontend
- **Framework**: React 18+ with Vite
- **Language**: TypeScript
- **Styling**: Tailwind CSS + Shadcn UI
- **Portals**:
  - **Admin Panel (`/Frontend`)**: For administration, consultant approval, and system management.
  - **User & Consultant Portal (`/TekConsult-user`)**: For end-users to book sessions and consultants to manage their dashboard.
- **Icons**: Lucide React
- **State Management**: React Context API
- **Real-time**: @microsoft/signalr (SignalR Client)

